  "detailed_description": "<strong>BRIDGE CROSSING</strong><br>Use a powerful barrier to pass through a large amount of projectiles<br>Bridge Crossing is an indie 2D pixel art game about a shepherd who must rescue his lost sheep from a war-torn bridge. You'll need intelligence, skill and courage to face the obstacles on your way, each stage representing a segment of the bridge under cannon fire. You'll also have to avoid collisions with other animals fleeing the chaos.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/130c3ed2e064e9dd2b2e7b09d27cf202.poster.avif?t=1715259388\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/130c3ed2e064e9dd2b2e7b09d27cf202.webm?t=1715259388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/130c3ed2e064e9dd2b2e7b09d27cf202.mp4?t=1715259388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Cross a wide bridge in search of your lost sheep<br><br><u>Gameplay</u><br>Walk through limited space to dodge cannonballs and wild boars<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/7e2961ce85b2b34db94eb27c8e62c6c8.poster.avif?t=1715259388\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/7e2961ce85b2b34db94eb27c8e62c6c8.webm?t=1715259388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/7e2961ce85b2b34db94eb27c8e62c6c8.mp4?t=1715259388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Unlock and use skills that will help you dodge projectiles!<br><u>Dash:</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/fbe9959bdbd50edf19dad998fb74c276.poster.avif?t=1715259388\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/fbe9959bdbd50edf19dad998fb74c276.webm?t=1715259388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/fbe9959bdbd50edf19dad998fb74c276.mp4?t=1715259388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Greater agility in your movement<br><br><u>Intangible:</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/39b903bd8cf7900641bcda83d9ab8bf9.poster.avif?t=1715259388\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/39b903bd8cf7900641bcda83d9ab8bf9.webm?t=1715259388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/39b903bd8cf7900641bcda83d9ab8bf9.mp4?t=1715259388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Become momentarily invulnerable to projectiles<br><br><u>Shield:</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/e8a12dd88ff73aa9e81e8bb7f65b77f2.poster.avif?t=1715259388\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/e8a12dd88ff73aa9e81e8bb7f65b77f2.webm?t=1715259388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/e8a12dd88ff73aa9e81e8bb7f65b77f2.mp4?t=1715259388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game combines puzzle and action elements. Can you save your sheep and make it back home? Test your limits in Bridge Crossing, an exciting and fun game!",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>BRIDGE CROSSING</strong><br>Use a powerful barrier to pass through a large amount of projectiles<br>Bridge Crossing is an indie 2D pixel art game about a shepherd who must rescue his lost sheep from a war-torn bridge. You'll need intelligence, skill and courage to face the obstacles on your way, each stage representing a segment of the bridge under cannon fire. You'll also have to avoid collisions with other animals fleeing the chaos.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/130c3ed2e064e9dd2b2e7b09d27cf202.poster.avif?t=1715259388\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/130c3ed2e064e9dd2b2e7b09d27cf202.webm?t=1715259388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/130c3ed2e064e9dd2b2e7b09d27cf202.mp4?t=1715259388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Cross a wide bridge in search of your lost sheep<br><br><u>Gameplay</u><br>Walk through limited space to dodge cannonballs and wild boars<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/7e2961ce85b2b34db94eb27c8e62c6c8.poster.avif?t=1715259388\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/7e2961ce85b2b34db94eb27c8e62c6c8.webm?t=1715259388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503240/extras/7e2961ce85b2b34db94eb27c8e62c6c8.mp4?t=1715259388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Unlock and use skills that will help you dodge projectiles!<br><u>Dash:</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" auto